## Task 1: Introduction
<ul>
<li>Understand what a web app is and how it runs in web browser.</li>
<li>Break down components of URL and see how it helps access web resources.</li>
<li>Learn how HTTP requests and responses work.</li>
<li>Get familiar with different types of HTTP request methods.</li>
<li>Understand what different HTTP response codes mean.</li>
<li>Check out how HTTP headers work and why they matter for security.</li>
</ul>

